{"tid":691900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政Whats噏：首缺席六四晚會　梁耀忠轟國泰累事","createTime":"2018-06-06T06:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T15:03:10.000Z","uid":6604,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"302f7c17c11c06147a70b954976268686ffc4c84","tid":691900,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:58:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">因管理不善而從全球最佳航空公司排名榜排名節節下跌</span>的國泰航空，服務又出問題，令支聯會常委、街工立法會議員梁耀忠缺席前天(4日)的六四燭光晚會，是他29年來首次缺席。梁耀忠斥國泰航空安排差，訊息混亂，令他困在機艙內5小時，對未能出席晚會感到不開心。 <br />\n<br />\n六四29年來，支聯會傳統於六四當日下午舉辦論壇晚上集會，梁耀忠過去多年亦無缺席。據了解，梁耀忠於六四前約一周，向支聯會常委表示因有急事不能主持論壇，但會出席晚會。梁耀忠今(6日)親述情況，指他上周六(2日)早上到台北，至本周一(4日)下午約3時許，乘國泰航班CX467返港，原訂下午5時許抵達，航機卻延誤5小時至晚上10時許才飛抵香港。 <br />\n<br />\n他續稱，當日登機後才有廣播通知，因天氣問題需延誤，一度稱只延誤約3小時，最終卻等了5小時，期間有乘客下機，航班又要移泊位。他批評國泰「安排好差」，令乘客在機上「困獸鬥」，不知何時才可飛，訊息很混亂，更沒有其他特別安排，只提供雞肉卷作晚餐，且沒有任何賠償。東網正向國泰查詢，暫未接獲回覆。 <br />\n<br />\n對於有指缺席集會是避免因支聯會綱領影響日後參選，梁耀忠稱，過去多年來都是認同支聯會綱領，亦有參加今年六四遊行，重申任何口號都會繼續嗌。 <br />\n<br />\n《國泰航空，愈做愈燶》專頁：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/fea/cx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Ffea%2Fcx%2F&d=TTCSStd0SLCqKvy40WHKmkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e5fd153d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/fea/cx/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n百份咁都有位入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b28abdae862b8dd56ff7e1292d0ec8897ef878e","tid":691900,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民打手真俊華</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/150218_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F150218_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=cce95e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千古罪人街工梁耀忠</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/500008/2?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/500008/2?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"b775ba8b23558ce351189ea2591bcdad013f703e","tid":691900,"uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:16:27.000Z","msg":"有冇新東巴絲諗住補選時射落海<br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/492309/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/492309/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n <br />\n睇關囝 cap 圖不如睇返我個原 post <br />\n等各巴打絲打自己諗下係咪好似本土派KOL關囝咁講"},{"pid":"f8fa4dbdaeb931ca59ab57e194f1d069b4ce16a7","tid":691900,"uid":6604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6b28abdae862b8dd56ff7e1292d0ec8897ef878e","tid":691900,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民打手真俊華</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/150218_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F150218_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=cce95e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千古罪人街工梁耀忠</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/500008/2?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/500008/2?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:18:53.000Z","msg":"你冇去尖咀係咪都係因航累你？<br />\n就算冇梁耀忠呢條柒頭，梁頌恒、游B、羅冠聰、劉小麗、姚松炎同長毛係咪唔會畀港共 DQ?"},{"pid":"031ed4732b2324fe293c6109d9b2be7c794dd1c5","tid":691900,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:19:25.000Z","msg":"on.99：因航令六四不能平反<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6a63a1e474f5c7e7703783a2af10e64a6988f5","tid":691900,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor